{"tid":530391,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"冇圖 短文 附懶人包 北上華強修理\"顯卡\"中伏遊","createTime":"2018-01-15T17:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T12:01:03.000Z","uid":131980,"like":102,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"81ff108dcf4255f53e25953a0afdaa374f5582dd","tid":530391,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">WARNING</span></strong></span>:<br />\n有時間就睇長文,無時間就睇懶人包,完.<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">懶人包</span></span></strong>:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">起因</span>-話說張顯示卡壞左,我唔小心撞爆左PCB<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經過</span>-之後北上華強修卡,150人仔修理完,走得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">結果</span>-張卡用到,不HDMI輸出唔到,過熱會重開<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n1快(1個鐘)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2真係修到,至少有畫面先啦(即場試,可惜跑唔到分)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3平(我覺得)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n1修完個樣比想像中差好撚遠,仲以為係自己修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2修理方法純靠自己經驗,無高科技儀器(預左)<br />\n3無咩靚女,全部死毒撚(預左)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">---完---<br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長文慎閱-主線任務</span><br />\n<br />\n是咁的,琴日打打下機好唔小心撞撚爆左顯示卡條邊,黑屏無畫面,風扇唔轉.<br />\n心諗仆街,用左半年都無唔通又要買卡?之後上連登乞討各位巴打意見.<br />\n可惜回應唔係比人恥笑就係賤格回收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好撚忟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此POST附圖一張:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/527432/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/527432/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/225752_e5e92a2afb02de23ef3d685a8e2213df.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F225752_e5e92a2afb02de23ef3d685a8e2213df.gif&h=6f754f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFINE,上連登,勿認真.靠人不如靠父幹,冇圖比人屌老母.<br />\nR撚哂HEAD o既時候,突然諗到北上華強呢個念頭.<br />\n我對華強認知好少:深圳某一忽,海量電子零件回收,買賣,鬼佬係道砌到部I PHONE<br />\n諗左一陣就決定左去.<br />\n<br />\n去之前緊係要計劃,上網GOOGLE左一陣,法國你老未華強唔洗咁撚大阿,唔知幾多個黃金.<br />\n(500平方呎VS2.9 平方公里,個比較係唔公平架喇,唔爽歡迎留正評表示反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/225708_8ab237ccd445400742d10bbb2b0b9bfd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F225708_8ab237ccd445400742d10bbb2b0b9bfd.png&h=8d31cbc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n掌握左半生熟o既地圖觀後就出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事前我聯絡左好多個修卡師傳,金銀銅鑽石大師菁英級都有,唔同價錢,唔同地方,最後搵左個係華強擺檔o既深山修練十年老經驗江湖五星級修卡大師傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOK出發,B3X到深圳灣過關後坐90路大巴到世界之窗地鐵站搭去華強路站<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/231811_c9918472e93476492891a86576dd7ab5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F231811_c9918472e93476492891a86576dd7ab5.jpeg&h=c79b4a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/231819_0c11033cbf63b70d618c26dace16b501.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F231819_0c11033cbf63b70d618c26dace16b501.jpeg&h=c43ffc56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到華強路站後我就去A出口<br />\n右邊果幾個呀叔SELL緊偷聽器生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/232730_af03678ddbac141b14785183b4ec48b3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F232730_af03678ddbac141b14785183b4ec48b3.jpeg&h=12e6e919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行多幾步又撞到鬼佬,呢道好撚多鬼佬,東歐西歐巴基印度黑人金絲長腿咩都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/234458_5aa657b437fc3c093c3f8a95f86472c6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F234458_5aa657b437fc3c093c3f8a95f86472c6.jpeg&h=1053d970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再行轉左就到一條大路通華強(SORRY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚蒙)<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/235154_4603897453c8bb79840ceb34bb56a74f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F235154_4603897453c8bb79840ceb34bb56a74f.jpeg&h=34758e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張相左邊就係華強電子世界,有3棟,深圳一,二店同埋老華強.一二店賣新野,老華強賣舊野<br />\n最高果棟無記錯係二店,我就尻行左入去.格局同黃金差唔多啦,周圍o既店員會熱情問你個毒撚(姐係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )靚仔係咪砌機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> in普通話.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/001342_bf7c423b85612c2902cf8eaf6e2e50a1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F001342_bf7c423b85612c2902cf8eaf6e2e50a1.jpeg&h=a8bb1cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誤打誤撞,不經不過,突然有個醬爆樣o既人問我係唔係之前聯絡去修卡果條友<br />\n我話係搵鋪修顯示卡,佢R撚左2下頭,望住我黑人問號,顯示卡?我先諗起係叫顯卡,之後佢就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,就係咁樣,我就好唔小心地搵到師傳檔野<br />\n入面我無咩點影,因為有少少趕去其他地方<br />\n呢道提下你,華強呢邊o的鋪頭通常早10晚6,好準時走架<br />\n張卡比左師傅後佢就坐係位搞搞搞搞搞,我就去其他地方.<br />\n去左一陣再搵返去張卡就搞撚掂,我睇到扯哂旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/001923_1febff0358b6cb3188363dd29569e225.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F001923_1febff0358b6cb3188363dd29569e225.jpeg&h=9a0343e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好不幸佢部測試機點撚樣都裝唔系到個顯示卡DRIVER,佢又趕住收工,唯有拎返屋企試.<br />\n係喎唔記得左,搵佢果陣佢係報80蚊,到左就話罰我因為唔識照顧顯示卡所以收多我70蚊.咁我唯有照比啦<br />\n當我接住師傅比我果陣卡o既時候,我用充滿無限FF,覺得深圳維修好撚正,歡喜咁慢慢向下望住自己手渣住o既果張顯示卡,個心同自己講,嘩呢個師傅好撚柒勁呀,咁撚後生識咁多野,加上佢無憂o既眼神,係幾咁出眾獨特,直頭拍撚得住果o的咩日本業餘工藝師.我果刻真係好期待,好興奮.<br />\n做好心理準備去欣賞大師傑作,係點搞架呢,係邊一回事呢.<br />\n當我一反轉張顯示卡,望撚到咁o既樣,我就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係有少少想一蚊都唔比就走.係修好,但點解樣衰左咁多....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/004716_13d4b97371341cdd2206c07708291a11.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F004716_13d4b97371341cdd2206c07708291a11.jpeg&h=76965506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/004721_22f28811ed3b437ce4a33c488b4c3d21.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F004721_22f28811ed3b437ce4a33c488b4c3d21.jpeg&h=4766c7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFINE,樣衰無問題,我安慰自己打機無問題就無問題.<br />\n點知..真係無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,但就有呢2個問題,HDMI無畫面同過熱會DETECT唔到之後898之後要重開機.<br />\n宜家用呢張卡我都開100%FAN SPEED.少少嘈,不過可以正常使用. <br />\n希望唔會有其他問題啦...<br />\n師傅唔係收完錢就唔認人o既,佢比左佢wechat我,話有問題就聯絡佢,佢幫我搞.<br />\n<br />\n華強技術,你永遠捉摸唔到<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">---主線任務-完---</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">支線任務</span><br />\n<br />\n好喇,我修卡之外,第二樣野就係退番啦on9 CPU比個賣家,用3底板去TEST都係唔著,同佢講好似我屈尻佢o的CPU係壞咁.順路之際,我就搵上門,到佢鋪位TEST果粒垃圾去證明自己.<br />\n檔野係老華強,我搵到佢後就叫佢TEST,最後係證實粒野係壞,佢地就啞狗咁款同我道歉,我話我要報警,佢話唔好話送粒好o既比我.咁我大人不計小人過,就接受左佢地o既道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/005529_5a088e3b4111e54dad7378e6aaa5f22b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F005529_5a088e3b4111e54dad7378e6aaa5f22b.jpeg&h=d8200423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/005536_4e839c66e15b511c1d98a1457f5301d2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F005536_4e839c66e15b511c1d98a1457f5301d2.jpeg&h=543869d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">---支線任務-完---</div>"},{"pid":"8570288a3efdb071400913bd42007512def4f865","tid":530391,"uid":131980,"like":17,"dislike":5,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:03:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">食 拍攝</span><br />\n<br />\n做任務之外緊係影下相食下野留念,唔多講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/010212_e61810b5ceb7ea6faa8c50d33a79fa2d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F010212_e61810b5ceb7ea6faa8c50d33a79fa2d.jpeg&h=1b21a7a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/010219_a053936edafd969f76484536d64a5b86.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F010219_a053936edafd969f76484536d64a5b86.jpeg&h=a3fb01ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/010223_6a35f2aefd4d3de6d7c370482f9233b4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F010223_6a35f2aefd4d3de6d7c370482f9233b4.jpeg&h=83c094aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/010228_d72f3faa8cc379e7af291cc018f33081.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F010228_d72f3faa8cc379e7af291cc018f33081.jpeg&h=52c765de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/010235_35f747255e86a120353762b33c2e33a3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F010235_35f747255e86a120353762b33c2e33a3.jpeg&h=8f48d4a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a0c0358c51a5e0be613a459793f22b6fdb8dafd","tid":530391,"uid":82970,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"正皮係比有心機打篇野覺得好耐都冇睇過啲咁既旅遊post，負皮係比點解樓豬由頭柒到落尾仲要俾人罰埋錢，睇黎店主一係就愛卡之人一係就商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d7284e75dd2d33e2da6779d30b23e9b21f7d15","tid":530391,"uid":91146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:16:56.000Z","msg":"食味千拉麵？"},{"pid":"c806b0d2b3177cb29